                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-221-18401123 t18401123-221-punishment-197"></join>Transported for Ten Years</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">ELIZABETH O'BRIEN</hi>—<hi rend="largeCaps">
                     <rs id="t18401123-221-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
